      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "A charming fair-condition classic with plenty of vintage style and solid potential for someone who wants an affordable entry into the hobby. This car presents as a usable driver with the kind of honest wear you\u2019d expect at this level, and it\u2019s a good candidate to enjoy as-is while improving over time. Not a show car, but a straightforward, appealing classic with character and room to make it your own.",
