    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Well-kept vehicle in good overall condition. The exterior shows normal cosmetic wear for its age and use, including a few small blemishes and light signs of regular driving, but it still presents very nicely. The interior is clean and solid overall with typical wear on commonly used surfaces, nothing out of line for a vehicle of this age. This is an honest, good-condition driver that appears to have been maintained and should be a strong option for someone looking for a dependable vehicle without expecting a showroom-perfect example.",
